window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Don't miss <i>The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones,</i> soon to be a major motion picture, in theaters August 2013.</b> </p> <p>Danger intensifies for the Shadowhunters as the <i>New York Times</i> best-selling Infernal Devices trilogy comes to a close. </p> <p>If the only way to save the world was to destroy what you loved most, would you do it? </p> <p>The clock is ticking. Everyone must choose. </p> <p>Passion. Power. Secrets. Enchantment. </p> <p>Danger closes in around the Shadowhunters in the final installment of the best-selling Infernal Devices trilogy.</p>"; 
